{"tid":1927123,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想交稅可以睇下合唔合符資格試下申請緩繳暫繳稅","createTime":"2020-03-15T14:43:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T08:25:00.000Z","uid":89139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"49bf52867278e8c72bc8b813b18cff4050331829","tid":1927123,"uid":89139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:43:54.000Z","msg":"無論係利得稅/薪俸稅/物業稅, 最簡單一個條件就係你在暫繳稅課稅年度的應課稅入息實額，少於或可能會少於前一年度的應課稅入息實額的90 %，又或少於或可能會少於暫繳稅課稅年度估計入息的90%。<br />\n<br />\n例子參考:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ird.gov.hk/chi/faq/hpt.htm#a1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ird.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Ffaq%2Fhpt.htm%23a1&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=f4546e6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ird.gov.hk/chi/faq/hpt.htm#a1</a><br />\n<br />\n申請表格(需要用IE開):(英文版)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ird.gov.hk/eng/pdf/ir1121e.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ird.gov.hk%2Feng%2Fpdf%2Fir1121e.pdf&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=83f2a2e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ird.gov.hk/eng/pdf/ir1121e.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n(中文版)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ird.gov.hk/chi/pdf/ir1121c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ird.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fpdf%2Fir1121c.pdf&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=c0d9d815\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ird.gov.hk/chi/pdf/ir1121c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nFB有POST都提及過緩繳暫繳稅<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/taxresistancehk/photos/a.315421001982620/1096792513845461/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftaxresistancehk%2Fphotos%2Fa.315421001982620%2F1096792513845461%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=c1676ae2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/taxresistancehk/photos/a.315421001982620/1096792513845461/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n有咩問題都可以係到討論下, 盡量解答"},{"pid":"2cb4e205289149c2909e3144fb87d49067cf8f64","tid":1927123,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T15:11:03.000Z","msg":"其實財政預算案公俺畸峎稅<br />\n我仲需唔需要返埋下期暫繳稅？定照交完等佢退返？"},{"pid":"b80c5ccdb2c0121cdcb93a132ee4d080360124db","tid":1927123,"uid":2247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T15:34:50.000Z","msg":"第一年報物業稅冇tick 到計埋入個人入息計 收到稅單嚇死我 請問要點樣要求重審<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40685593f5920ab7237d38aac7e3aae3842bd393","tid":1927123,"uid":89139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cb4e205289149c2909e3144fb87d49067cf8f64","tid":1927123,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T15:11:03.000Z","msg":"其實財政預算案公俺畸峎稅<br />\n我仲需唔需要返埋下期暫繳稅？定照交完等佢退返？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T21:30:12.000Z","msg":"你既預繳稅係唔會扣下期財政預算案既稅款寬減<br />\n<br />\n稅款寬減只會扣你今年要交既稅"},{"pid":"6a30814deda2545f7aa3c7e1db679bc992982159","tid":1927123,"uid":89139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b80c5ccdb2c0121cdcb93a132ee4d080360124db","tid":1927123,"uid":2247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T15:34:50.000Z","msg":"第一年報物業稅冇tick 到計埋入個人入息計 收到稅單嚇死我 請問要點樣要求重審<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T21:39:01.000Z","msg":"其實你合併有機會交少D稅,因為物業稅統一15%<br />\n但係個人稅progressive rate由2%到17%都有<br />\n如果交standard rate 15%就無分別<br />\n合唔合併要多D數據計下先知<br />\n<br />\n重審有時限,參考網址<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.hk/en/residents/taxes/taxfiling/object/objections.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Fen%2Fresidents%2Ftaxes%2Ftaxfiling%2Fobject%2Fobjections.htm&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=52666e73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.hk/en/residents/taxes/taxfiling/object/objections.htm</a>"},{"pid":"fb72c63f202374dc13ce69e8bd468539be44918b","tid":1927123,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:25:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}